headline: Previously unknown Picasso portrait revealed in Paris
description: The colorful oil painting, entitled 'Bust of a woman with a flowery hat,' depicts Dora Maar, an artist and Pablo Picasso's muse. It is being put up for auction in Paris, with a reserve price of €8 million.
